Client is the same expect:
1. added some error checking
2. when connection to server succeed, client will send its username to server
3. when quitchat with enter typed, it will exit

To run the program
make server
make client
server [username] [portnumber](optional)
client [username] [ipaddress](optional) [portnumber](optional)

for client to leave, type quitchat with an enter


